I have so many things and ideas I want to share. Not necessarily workouts or programs but more of mental jewels that might help ppl gtfo of bed or make that change they know they should. I’ve learned a lot the past 2 years. I know the feeling and our time here is to short to go hating life. I know you see the professional mic on the shirt and the professional camera lol… new workout vlog dropping soon on YouTube. I’m hype for this new journey.

📸: @landostudios1

I’ve never been more focused. Seriously feel like I’ve found a purpose lately with my platforms and I can’t wait to share it all over these next few months. Going to be a long journey but I’m so blessed to do this and thank y’all for the support. 🙏🏻

NEW YOUTUBE VIDEO LIVE. Link in bio.

📸: @landostudios1

Day 12!! It’s easy when you just DECIDE enough is enough but god damn time is going slow…. I’m proud of myself but this is by no means an absolute cure. Had a rough 2 days mentally for absolutely no reason but I still got the f*** up and did what I needed to do. The old NiaC would NEVER. Learning to simply observe these negative times/thoughts instead of indentifying myself as them. There’s still work to be done and a long journey ahead. New vlog dropping tonight and another workout video tomorrow. Reels too 😲📈💜

📸 @landostudios1

we have evolved from millions of years of MOVEMENT… no wonder our brains are losing their fkn mind being stationary. Who knows what this is doing to our brain chemistry. Our generation is the Guinea pigs of not having to move a muscle to live but idk if it’s a life worth living. 💭📈

this best part about it… y’all getting me thru it and I’m hoping to return the favor. Actually imma be honest, I’m at the point of my life where I’m not even giving myself an option TO NOT GET THE FKN JOB DONE. JOIN ME IN DOING THE SAME WHETHER MOTIVATED OR NOT WE MUST ACCOMPLISH OUR GOAL FOR ONCE IN OUR FKN LIVES. THIS IS WHEN WE START FEELING GOOD AND OUR LIVES FKN STARTING CHANGING FOR THE BETTER

#gym #fitness #bodybuilding #motivation #mentalhealthawareness

WE GOT GOALS TO ACHIEVE

WE’VE STOPPED WHEN UNCOMFORTABLE AND TIRED OUR WHOLE LIVES. LOOK WHERE THAT GOT US! 

START NOW GOGOGOGO

the change in how you feel doesn’t happen instantly but soon enough you’ll start getting a sense of accomplishment for showing up. Some of our success is going to start small but a small start is sometimes enough to start enjoying life again. Learning to enjoy this journey. 📈

One of the greatest things I’ve learned in the past few years is that when we’re depressed and anxious we DEPRESS into a tight shallow breathing person. By being conscious of that we can fight it by opening up and EXPRESSING ourselves as humans. Breathing, opening, stretching and relaxing our bodies, changing the brain chemistry of our minds. Do not depress, EXPRESS. Day 28
